Data set source: 
http://cs.joensuu.fi/sipu/datasets/ 

Description: 
Synthetic two dimensional data with 5000 observations and fifteen 
(K = 15) Gaussian clusters with different degree of cluster overlap.

Reference:
P. Frðnti and S. Sieranoja, "K-means properties on six clustering 
    benchmark datasets" Applied Intelligence, 48 (12), 4743-4759, 
    December 2018

